Error_start-missing: The first part of the range is not set
Error_end-missing: The second part of the range is not set
Error_incomplete-range: You must specify both parts of the range
Error_min: The first part of the range less than minimum
Error_max: The second part of the range greater than maximum
Error_incorrect-start: The first part of the range is specified incorrectly
Error_incorrect-end: The second part of the range is specified incorrectly
